      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NEXT BLACK JACK (2) was quickly out of the boxes with a slick early sectional clocking 23.63 with a one length win at this track over 407m. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to his name from six starts. Looks the one to beat. WAKA WAKA (1) scored two back then well held latest finishing a 12 length 7th at this track (30.69). Can figure in the finish. GOLDEN ENVY (4) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (23.65) at this track behind Roxy Cambla in a Free For All. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Expecting another good run. WANGAROA WALLY (6) was below best last time at this track (24.15) in a Free For All, finishing a 4 length fourth. Already a winner from this draw.",
